{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 7,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 350.367,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.322,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I would that ye might know",
      "verse": "7:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 2.502,
      "end": 7.053,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that after my father, Lehi, had made an end of prophesying",
      "verse": "7:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 7.233,
      "end": 8.905,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning his seed,",
      "verse": "7:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 9.085,
      "end": 12.382,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it came to pass that the Lord spake unto him again, saying",
      "verse": "7:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 12.562,
      "end": 14.884,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it was not meet for him, Lehi,",
      "verse": "7:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 15.064,
      "end": 18.733,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he should take his family into the wilderness alone;",
      "verse": "7:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 18.913,
      "end": 22.117,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but that his sons should take daughters to wife,",
      "verse": "7:1",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 22.297,
      "end": 26.012,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they might raise up seed unto the Lord in the land of promise.",
      "verse": "7:1",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 26.692,
      "end": 29.618,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the Lord commanded him",
      "verse": "7:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 29.798,
      "end": 35.324,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I, Nephi, and my brethren, should again return unto the land of Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "7:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 35.504,
      "end": 38.848,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and bring down Ishmael and his family into the wilderness.",
      "verse": "7:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 39.528,
      "end": 43.522,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, did again, with my brethren,",
      "verse": "7:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 43.702,
      "end": 46.767,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "go forth into the wilderness to go up to Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "7:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 47.447,
      "end": 51.162,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we went up unto the house of Ishmael,",
      "verse": "7:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 51.342,
      "end": 54.732,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we did gain favor in the sight of Ishmael,",
      "verse": "7:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 54.912,
      "end": 58.163,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that we did speak unto him the words of the Lord.",
      "verse": "7:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 58.843,
      "end": 63.301,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the Lord did soften the heart of Ishmael,",
      "verse": "7:5",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 63.481,
      "end": 65.106,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also his household,",
      "verse": "7:5",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 65.286,
      "end": 70.116,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that they took their journey with us down into the wilderness",
      "verse": "7:5",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 70.296,
      "end": 71.921,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to the tent of our father.",
      "verse": "7:5",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 72.601,
      "end": 76.13,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that as we journeyed in the wilderness,",
      "verse": "7:6",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 76.31,
      "end": 78.121,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold Laman and Lemuel,",
      "verse": "7:6",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 78.301,
      "end": 80.391,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and two of the daughters of Ishmael",
      "verse": "7:6",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 80.571,
      "end": 83.775,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the two sons of Ishmael and their families,",
      "verse": "7:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 83.955,
      "end": 85.72,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "did rebel against us;",
      "verse": "7:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 85.9,
      "end": 88.501,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, against me, Nephi, and Sam,",
      "verse": "7:6",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 88.681,
      "end": 91.049,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their father, Ishmael, and his wife,",
      "verse": "7:6",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 91.229,
      "end": 93.087,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and his three other daughters.",
      "verse": "7:6",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 93.767,
      "end": 96.368,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass in the which rebellion,",
      "verse": "7:7",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 96.548,
      "end": 100.403,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they were desirous to return unto the land of Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "7:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 101.083,
      "end": 104.845,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, being grieved for the hardness of their hearts,",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 105.025,
      "end": 107.301,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "therefore I spake unto them, saying,",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 107.481,
      "end": 110.36,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even unto Laman and unto Lemuel:",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 110.54,
      "end": 113.001,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold ye are mine elder brethren,",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 113.181,
      "end": 115.503,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and how is it that ye are so hard",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 115.683,
      "end": 118.469,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in your hearts, and so blind in your minds,",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 118.649,
      "end": 121.807,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye have need that I, your younger brother,",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 121.987,
      "end": 123.612,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should speak unto you,",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 123.792,
      "end": 126.068,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, and set an example for you?",
      "verse": "7:8",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 126.748,
      "end": 130.695,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "How is it that ye have not hearkened unto the word of the Lord?",
      "verse": "7:9",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 131.375,
      "end": 133.604,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "How is it that ye have forgotten",
      "verse": "7:10",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 133.784,
      "end": 136.106,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye have seen an angel of the Lord?",
      "verse": "7:10",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 136.786,
      "end": 139.247,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, and how is it that ye have forgotten",
      "verse": "7:11",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 139.427,
      "end": 142.213,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "what great things the Lord hath done for us,",
      "verse": "7:11",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 142.393,
      "end": 145.412,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in delivering us out of the hands of Laban,",
      "verse": "7:11",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 145.592,
      "end": 147.775,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also that we should obtain the record?",
      "verse": "7:11",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 148.455,
      "end": 150.916,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, and how is it that ye have forgotten",
      "verse": "7:12",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 151.096,
      "end": 153.836,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord is able to do all things",
      "verse": "7:12",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 154.016,
      "end": 157.174,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to his will, for the children of men,",
      "verse": "7:12",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 157.354,
      "end": 160.048,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if it so be that they exercise faith in him?",
      "verse": "7:12",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 160.228,
      "end": 162.411,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, let us be faithful to him.",
      "verse": "7:12",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 163.091,
      "end": 165.645,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And if it so be that we are faithful to him,",
      "verse": "7:13",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 165.825,
      "end": 168.24,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we shall obtain the land of promise;",
      "verse": "7:13",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 168.42,
      "end": 171.114,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and ye shall know at some future period",
      "verse": "7:13",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 171.294,
      "end": 173.941,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the word of the Lord shall be fulfilled",
      "verse": "7:13",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 174.121,
      "end": 176.629,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the destruction of Jerusalem;",
      "verse": "7:13",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 176.809,
      "end": 179.317,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for all things which the Lord hath spoken",
      "verse": "7:13",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 179.497,
      "end": 182.887,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the destruction of Jerusalem must be fulfilled.",
      "verse": "7:13",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 183.567,
      "end": 189.465,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, the Spirit of the Lord ceaseth soon to strive with them;",
      "verse": "7:14",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 189.645,
      "end": 192.246,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, they have rejected the prophets,",
      "verse": "7:14",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 192.426,
      "end": 194.98,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and Jeremiah have they cast into prison.",
      "verse": "7:14",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 195.16,
      "end": 197.946,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they have sought to take away the life of my father,",
      "verse": "7:14",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 198.126,
      "end": 201.191,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that they have driven him out of the land.",
      "verse": "7:14",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 201.871,
      "end": 203.821,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now behold, I say unto you",
      "verse": "7:15",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 204.001,
      "end": 206.648,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that if ye will return unto Jerusalem",
      "verse": "7:15",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 206.828,
      "end": 209.011,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye shall also perish with them.",
      "verse": "7:15",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 209.191,
      "end": 211.745,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, if ye have choice, go up to the land,",
      "verse": "7:15",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 211.925,
      "end": 214.944,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and remember the words which I speak unto you",
      "verse": "7:15",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 215.124,
      "end": 217.632,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that if ye go ye will also perish;",
      "verse": "7:15",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 217.812,
      "end": 221.806,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for thus the Spirit of the Lord constraineth me that I should speak.",
      "verse": "7:15",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 222.486,
      "end": 227.13,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that when I, Nephi, had spoken these words unto my brethren,",
      "verse": "7:16",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 227.31,
      "end": 228.657,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they were angry with me.",
      "verse": "7:16",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 228.837,
      "end": 232.181,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that they did lay their hands upon me,",
      "verse": "7:16",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 232.361,
      "end": 234.915,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, they were exceedingly wroth,",
      "verse": "7:16",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 235.095,
      "end": 237.278,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they did bind me with cords,",
      "verse": "7:16",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 237.458,
      "end": 239.966,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they sought to take away my life,",
      "verse": "7:16",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 240.146,
      "end": 243.165,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they might leave me in the wilderness",
      "verse": "7:16",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 243.345,
      "end": 245.621,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to be devoured by wild beasts.",
      "verse": "7:16",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 246.301,
      "end": 249.366,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But it came to pass that I prayed unto the Lord, saying:",
      "verse": "7:17",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 249.546,
      "end": 250.521,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O Lord,",
      "verse": "7:17",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 250.701,
      "end": 253.116,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to my faith which is in thee,",
      "verse": "7:17",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 253.296,
      "end": 256.315,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wilt thou deliver me from the hands of my brethren;",
      "verse": "7:17",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 256.495,
      "end": 258.353,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even give me strength",
      "verse": "7:17",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 258.533,
      "end": 261.644,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I may burst these bands with which I am bound.",
      "verse": "7:17",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 262.324,
      "end": 265.482,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that when I had said these words,",
      "verse": "7:18",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 265.662,
      "end": 268.866,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, the bands were loosed from off my hands and feet,",
      "verse": "7:18",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 269.046,
      "end": 271.136,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I stood before my brethren,",
      "verse": "7:18",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 271.316,
      "end": 273.174,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I spake unto them again.",
      "verse": "7:18",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 273.854,
      "end": 276.873,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that they were angry with me again,",
      "verse": "7:19",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 277.053,
      "end": 279.329,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and sought to lay hands upon me;",
      "verse": "7:19",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 279.509,
      "end": 282.481,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but behold, one of the daughters of Ishmael,",
      "verse": "7:19",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 282.661,
      "end": 284.472,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, and also her mother,",
      "verse": "7:19",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 284.652,
      "end": 286.835,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and one of the sons of Ishmael,",
      "verse": "7:19",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 287.015,
      "end": 289.012,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "did plead with my brethren,",
      "verse": "7:19",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 289.192,
      "end": 291.7,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that they did soften their hearts;",
      "verse": "7:19",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 291.88,
      "end": 295.177,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they did cease striving to take away my life.",
      "verse": "7:19",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 295.857,
      "end": 298.783,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that they were sorrowful,",
      "verse": "7:20",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 298.963,
      "end": 301.006,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of their wickedness,",
      "verse": "7:20",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 301.186,
      "end": 303.926,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that they did bow down before me,",
      "verse": "7:20",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 304.106,
      "end": 305.778,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and did plead with me",
      "verse": "7:20",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 305.958,
      "end": 310.091,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I would forgive them of the thing that they had done against me.",
      "verse": "7:20",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 310.771,
      "end": 315.694,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I did frankly forgive them all that they had done,",
      "verse": "7:21",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 315.874,
      "end": 318.521,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I did exhort them that they would pray",
      "verse": "7:21",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 318.701,
      "end": 321.069,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the Lord their God for forgiveness.",
      "verse": "7:21",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 321.249,
      "end": 323.478,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that they did so.",
      "verse": "7:21",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 323.658,
      "end": 326.537,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they had done praying unto the Lord",
      "verse": "7:21",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 326.717,
      "end": 329.178,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we did again travel on our journey",
      "verse": "7:21",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
